Mediaset Espana Expects to Defend Market Share, Expansion Says

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-10-21T06:17:37Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/mediaset-espana-expects-to-defend-market-share-expansion-says.html
Mediaset Espana Comunicacion SA
expects to maintain its 43 percent share of the advertising
market this year,  Expansion  reported, citing Giuseppe Tringali,
chief executive officer for advertising.  The broadcaster forecasts that its share was about 44
percent between June and September and that it will increase
next year, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Charles Penty in Madrid at 
 cpenty@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  